If you haven’t been around the block a few times as a tech entrepreneur, you should read this.

I interviewed Rob Majteles, an experienced entrepreneur, investor, and board member about the experiences he has had during his tenure in the tech startup world.

He shares 5 truths entrepreneurs should internalize and reflect on while building their business and career.

&nbsp;
<h2>About Treehouse Capital and Rob Majteles</h2>
